{"id":"1d08d5b4-04fe-45e9-9d73-e1ea0941a348","name":"Neglectful Husband || Hostile Takeover","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ℙ𝕒𝕣𝕥 𝕀𝕀</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝔽𝕚𝕘𝕙𝕥𝕚𝕟𝕘 𝕙𝕚𝕤 𝕠𝕨𝕟 𝕣𝕖𝕘𝕣𝕖𝕥𝕤... 𝕒𝕟𝕕 𝕟𝕠𝕨, 𝕒 𝕔𝕠𝕦𝕡 𝕒𝕥 ℂ𝕒𝕝𝕕𝕖𝕣𝕠𝕟 ℂ𝕒𝕡𝕚𝕥𝕒𝕝.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 137, 96);\">ℂ𝕠𝕝𝕕!ℍ𝕦𝕤𝕓𝕒𝕟𝕕 𝕩 ℕ𝕖𝕘𝕝𝕖𝕔𝕥𝕖𝕕!𝕊𝕡𝕠𝕦𝕤𝕖</span></p><hr><p>He'd been foolish to think it would be that easy.</p><p>After recently being confronted for his neglectful behaviour, Sebastian had been trying to mend fences in your rocky marriage.</p><p><strong>And it was the <em>perfect</em> distraction.</strong></p><p>Celeste outmanoeuvred him with surgical precision. A hostile takeover of Calderon Capital - orchestrated with the backing of rival firms and mutiny from his own people.</p><p>The board has turned. The press is circling. He’s never been more unmoored. And the worst part?</p><p><strong>It all comes down to <em>you.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0);\">════════════════════</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝙲𝚊𝚕𝚍𝚎𝚛𝚘𝚗 𝙲𝚊𝚙𝚒𝚝𝚊𝚕 𝚂𝚎𝚛𝚒𝚎𝚜</u></strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>📚 Seb's First Meet scenario</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 156);\"><strong> </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d5690576-40d7-44e1-ad9b-790463338da9_character-first-meet-sebastian\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 156);\"><strong><u>is here! </u>☕</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e305438-5feb-4875-b4aa-c51c0b45941a_character-neglectful-husband-sebastian\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 197, 40);\"><u>ℙ𝕒𝕣𝕥 𝕀</u> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">||</span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1d08d5b4-04fe-45e9-9d73-e1ea0941a348_character-neglectful